modules.description: Implements custom log message expansion through PPX rewriters, transforming log expressions into structured output. Works directly with OCaml AST nodes and extension contexts to generate efficient logging code. Enables compile-time processing of log statements for backends like `Logs` without runtime overhead.

Transforms log expressions into optimized structured output using PPX rewriters, operating directly on OCaml AST nodes and extension contexts. Enables compile-time generation of logging code compatible with backends like `Logs`, eliminating runtime overhead. Useful for embedding type-safe, efficient logging directly into OCaml applications during compilation.
